document_data.name: Schuyler
document_data.mainbody: '''Schuyler''' was a food critic  in [[Phlan]] during the [[Tyranny of Dragons]].
document_data.History: In [[1489 DR]], Schuyler went to the [[Madame Freona's Tea Kettle]] in order to test their food. She was briefly interrogated by adventurers hired by [[Buhrell Caah]] about a missing dangerous magical item.{{Cite adventurers league/Defiance in Phlan|24}}
